{
  "stem": "27748.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was totally scared of this woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I saw her coming, I would hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was totally scared of her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was always critical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this business you should become a watchmaker was just the last straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was totally intimidated, and in-- totally scared of this woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was in dread of her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was not a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was a dragon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the odd thing is, to the outside world, she was this humane person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she obviously was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She did do great things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she was also a person who couldn't relate on the personal, humane way in intimate ways.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, I sometimes think of Eleanor Roosevelt in that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Perhaps it's fair.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Perhaps it's not fair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Eleanor Roosevelt did these fantastic things for the world's humanity, for many suffering people, she stood up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I don't-- from what little I know, she was not very adept at intimacy with her immediate family, and anybody in-- well, anyway, so that-- in the [?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anna Essinger ?] situation, that's sort of the sense I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was a dragon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I thought of her as a monster, and the same person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I would hide when I saw her coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I certainly didn't feel like talking to her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the issues talking about-- talking about-- I don't remember anybody talking about what happened to my parents, what happened to our families, the other children or mine.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I don't remember at Bunce Court during those years confronting what we children were going through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't know what we were going through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but the point also was, the teachers themselves were immigrants who were themselves screwed up, and going through the trauma of trying to adjust.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
